{"tid":836284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖慎入] 建制泛民齊賀中秋　蔣麗芸修圖成嫦娥　陸頌雄扮美少女戰士稱「替月行道」","createTime":"2018-09-25T14:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T14:05:38.000Z","uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"248b109e85e9cc5ce7afbcfe5dc19e3c5871d70c","tid":836284,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:05:38.000Z","msg":"今日是一年一度中秋節。建制派及民主派多名議員，都有於社交網站發圖祝賀市民節日快樂，其中以民建聯蔣麗芸及工聯會陸頌雄最「別出心裁」。<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸早上於facebook發圖，驟眼看是抱着小白兔的嫦娥奔月圖，認真細看，「嫦娥」的臉與蔣麗芸有八、九分相似，相信是「真人入畫」，把自己頭像置於「嫦娥」身軀，的確有心思，更獲網民留言大讚「超美的嫦娥」。但亦有網民認為蔣麗芸過分抬舉自己，揶揄「萬聖節快樂」。<br />\n<br />\n說到創意，陸頌雄亦不遑多讓，於fb把自己的臉「移植」到日本動畫美少女戰士主角月野兔身軀上，稱要「替月行道」。他表示，2017年香港人浪費了227萬個月餅，「層層疊」高度接近100公里，期望大家今年不要浪費，「可以食多幾日，或者轉贈畀有需要嘅人」，並呼籲齊向月餅說「替月行道」、「代表月亮消滅你」。<br />\n<br />\n不過網民似乎不太受落，稱圖片令人不安，「童年幻滅」。陸頌雄亦特別標籤了「#溫馨提示 #食嘢時千祈唔好打開」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/220118_a46370425f16a282544d79edcb625dcc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F220118_a46370425f16a282544d79edcb625dcc.png&h=6be51b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/220410_37919a285b91a7408616e32b67988a4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F220410_37919a285b91a7408616e32b67988a4c.png&h=58f55cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180924/s00001/1537779318364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F1537779318364&d=eau1pT1Jp57XoavZcWmTRwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=03f9017a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F1537779318364&h=42cca894\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180924/s00001/1537779318364</a><br />\n<br />\nCLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}